WEBVTT

00:03.078 --> 00:05.193
[Creature howling]

00:05.194 --> 00:07.671
Whatever jumped off the back of my house,

00:07.672 --> 00:10.525
landed 20 feet out in
the middle of my yard.

00:10.526 --> 00:13.041
Nothing can do that.

00:13.042 --> 00:17.318
There was definitely
something inside that house.

00:17.319 --> 00:18.264
Stop!

00:18.265 --> 00:20.714
I know I'm not going nuts,

00:20.715 --> 00:25.786
but I'm seeing something, and
what I'm seeing is there, but...

00:25.787 --> 00:28.054
It's not.

00:28.055 --> 00:31.258
Something was out there, stalking me.

00:31.259 --> 00:33.899
[Dramatic music]

00:40.468 --> 00:43.108
[Haunting music]

